  title: "Can\u2019t Cinemachine do zooming automatically for 2D games?"
  text: "Not directly, unfortunately. While Cinemachine has some built-in 3D zoom
    features, for 2D orthographic zoom we need to manually change the `OrthographicSize`
    ourselves. Thankfully, it\u2019s easy to implement with a simple script and `Mathf.Lerp`."
